@using FrostlineECommerce.Models
@model List<DiscountViewModel>




<div class="btn btn-outline-primary">

        <a class="btn-btn-warning">@ViewBag.Period </a>
</div>

<table class="table">
    <thead>
        <tr>
            <th scope="col">Id</th>
            <th scope="col">Name</th>
            <th scope="col">PeriodName</th>
            <th scope="col">CategoryName</th>
            <th scope="col">DiscountRate</th>
            <th scope="col">StartDate</th>
            <th scope="col">EndDate</th>
            <th scope="col">IsActive</th>
            <th scope="col">Transactions</th>

        </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
        @foreach (var item in Model)
        {
            <tr>
                <th scope="row">@item.Id</th>
                <td>@item.Name</td>
                <td>@item.PeriodName</td>
                <td>@item.CategoryName</td>
                <td>@item.DiscountRate</td>
                <td>@item.StartDate</td>
                <td>@item.EndDate</td>
                <td>@item.IsActive</td>
                <td><a href="/Product/EditDiscount/@item.Id" class="btn-btn-warning">Edit</a></td>
            </tr>
        }

    </tbody>
</table>